examples.en: Young people easily imbibe bad habits.
We were delighted to imbibe fresh air.
examples.ru: Мы с наслаждением вдыхали свежий воздух.

examples.en: She imbibed vast quantities of coffee.
Such salts are easily imbibed by water.
examples.ru: Такие соли легко растворяются в воде.

examples.en: She had imbibed the traditions of her family.
